+# DispatchInputCompositionHighlightOptions Object
+
+* `backgroundColor` string (optional) - CSS color used to fill the composition
+  range. Defaults to transparent.
+* `underlineColor` string (optional) - CSS color used to draw the composition
+  underline. Defaults to transparent.
+* `textColor` string (optional) - CSS color used to draw the composition text
+  when Chromium composition foreground markers are enabled. Defaults to
+  transparent.
+* `underlineStyle` string (optional) - Can be `none`, `solid`, `dot`, `dash`, or
+  `squiggle`. Defaults to `solid` when `underlineColor`, `underlineStyle`, or
+  `thickness` is specified, otherwise `none`.
+* `thickness` string (optional) - Can be `none`, `thin`, or `thick`. Defaults to
+  `thin` when `underlineColor`, `underlineStyle`, or `thickness` is specified,
+  otherwise `none`.
