   Must be provided together with `replacementEnd`.
 * `replacementEnd` Integer (optional) - End offset of the replacement range.
   Must be provided together with `replacementStart`.
+* `highlight` boolean | [DispatchInputCompositionHighlightOptions](dispatch-input-composition-highlight-options.md) (optional) - Controls how Chromium paints the composition range. If omitted or `true`, Chromium's default composition highlight is used. If `false`, the composition range is kept active but its background, underline, and text highlight are transparent. If an object is provided, its style is applied to the composition range.
